Program: Outlook
Title: Human Rights in Uzbekistan
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbsfd
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
An interview with Craig Murray, former United Kingdom Ambassador to Uzbekistan who lost his job when he exposed severe human rights abuses. He describes some of the gruesome scenes he witnessed. Also, overcoming harassment. Talking with the people caught up in the recent Mumbai train bombings. Presenter: Heather Payton. Show less